short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: View Wolves of Rome NFT rarities on jpg.store.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Discover the hidden rarities of Wolves, Liches, Vampires, and Vault NFTs on jpg.store! Originally, these NFTs were minted without the four distinct rarity levels: Common, Rare, Epic, and Legendary. Therefore, this crucial information isn't visible in the metadata on the jpg.store marketplace, making it challenging for collectors and enthusiasts to identify the rarity of their NFTs at a glance. Our extension elegantly solves this problem by seamlessly integrating rarity information directly into the jpg.store interface, allowing you to effortlessly view the rarity of each NFT.
